  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.34,
      510.92,
      533.46,
      549.41
    ],
    "text": "Due to a developing low-level atmospheric disturbance in the vicinity of Sri Lanka, an increase in rainfall over the island is expected during the next few days.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      6.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.34,
      552.95,
      456.24,
      573.41
    ],
    "text": "Showers or thundershowers will occur at most places of the island after 1.00 pm.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold",
      "Iskoola Pota"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      5.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.34,
      576.47,
      462.48,
      595.73
    ],
    "text": "Showers are likely in the Western and Southern provinces during the morning too.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      4.079999923706055,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.34,
      604.01,
      534.01,
      653.35
    ],
    "text": "Heavy falls above 100 mm are likely at some places in Sabaragamuwa, Central, Uva, Southern and North-central provinces. Fairly heavy falls above 50 mm are likely at some places in other areas of the island.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      0.9599999785423279,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.34,
      656.89,
      533.42,
      694.15
    ],
    "text": "Misty conditions can be expected at some places in Central, Sabaragamuwa and Uva provinces during the early hours of the morning.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      5.039999961853027,
      9.119999885559082,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.34,
      697.93,
      533.28,
      771.46
    ],
    "text": "The general public is kindly requested to take adequate precautions to minimize damages caused by temporary localized strong winds and lightning during thundershowers.",
    "fonts": [
